{"tid":957290,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"工聯會吳秋北：毛誕是「中國人的聖誕節」","createTime":"2018-12-27T02:15:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-28T15:36:16.000Z","uid":184679,"like":7,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"dc1fb7776103bf125ae7dc43893cd42f52d453e8","tid":957290,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T02:15:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20181227/s00046/35921d55daab567bd82db2b4e82d5eff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20181227%2Fs00046%2F35921d55daab567bd82db2b4e82d5eff.jpg&h=1fb4461f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】近日大家都好開心咁慶祝緊聖誕節，唔少政界人士仲外遊緊；另一邊廂，工聯會會長吳秋北（圖）就語出驚人，話噚日係「毛主席誕辰125周年」，呢個先應該係「中國人的聖誕節」，仲話最好嘅紀念就係向主席學習！<br />\n<br />\n已故中共領袖毛澤東任內功與過，過去有唔少評論，而吳秋北就喺facebook貼文留言大讚毛主席。佢仲回應網民，話「毛主席是中國數千年一遇，不世出的傑出領袖，現代中國如沒有毛主席，我們可能仍在黑暗中摸索。所以怎評價都不為過！」<br />\n<br />\n吳秋北嘅聖誕論引發唔少人留言爭論，有網民問佢，係咪應該學習毛主席發動文化大革命奪權？話「身為中國人，枉你仲可以甘（咁）歌頌毛主席，你是中共人，我是中國人」。有網民就撐吳秋北，話「沒有毛主席，就沒有新中國」。<br />\n<br />\n據報道，內地唔鼓勵慶祝洋人節日，𠵱家吳秋北就叫人慶祝毛主席「聖誕節」。不過，佢嘅黨友似乎無咁執著，好似麥美娟議員，平安夜就喺街頭向小朋友送上禮物，祝大家過快樂聖誕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20181227/s00002/1545848610599/%E5%90%B3%E7%A7%8B%E5%8C%97-%E6%AF%9B%E8%AA%95%E6%98%AF%E3%80%8C%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%BA%BA%E8%81%96%E8%AA%95%E7%AF%80%E3%80%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20181227%2Fs00002%2F1545848610599%2F%25E5%2590%25B3%25E7%25A7%258B%25E5%258C%2597-%25E6%25AF%259B%25E8%25AA%2595%25E6%2598%25AF%25E3%2580%258C%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%2581%2596%25E8%25AA%2595%25E7%25AF%2580%25E3%2580%258D&d=i5rxKKHPmPy3CA6H%2Fw9zAi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=1baa441f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20181227%2Fs00002%2F1545848610599%2F%25E5%2590%25B3%25E7%25A7%258B%25E5%258C%2597-%25E6%25AF%259B%25E8%25AA%2595%25E6%2598%25AF%25E3%2580%258C%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%2581%2596%25E8%25AA%2595%25E7%25AF%2580%25E3%2580%258D&h=1c185cb2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20181227/s00002/1545848610599/%E5%90%B3%E7%A7%8B%E5%8C%97-%E6%AF%9B%E8%AA%95%E6%98%AF%E3%80%8C%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%BA%BA%E8%81%96%E8%AA%95%E7%AF%80%E3%80%8D</a>"},{"pid":"0dc98fc65b7fa86e86ba28edcc776995ace302e3","tid":957290,"uid":4917,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T02:16:31.000Z","msg":"毛澤東封聖<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b218ac5638130f33cc7ec61ec73641317d02a01","tid":957290,"uid":184679,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"0dc98fc65b7fa86e86ba28edcc776995ace302e3","tid":957290,"uid":4917,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T02:16:31.000Z","msg":"毛澤東封聖<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T02:17:52.000Z","msg":"教宗維尼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b888252a94463398e1ba471e37b8ad5462d10cf","tid":957290,"uid":49918,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T02:17:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f395e62b7be30691dea88b219db55d627875444d","tid":957290,"uid":23180,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T02:25:35.000Z","msg":"慶祝可以做D咩?<br />\n<br />\n重演批鬥樣板劇?慶祝鬥死支那人??<br />\n<br />\n人有多大膽，地有多大產??<br />\n<br />\n寧要核子不要褲子?"},{"pid":"e5dba547f4438f2bc07fb439ab22c601291d45fd","tid":957290,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T02:26:11.000Z","msg":"真係痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c3755cfc39277f04f51fdd4b45261dd816b70b8","tid":957290,"uid":89931,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T02:26:27.000Z","msg":"無產階級大團結萬歲 打倒鄧小平修正主義<img src=\"/assets/face